\[\begin{align*}
  &L(\hat{y}, y) = (y-\hat{y})^2
\end{align*}\]






Logistic regression, binary targets


\[\begin{align*}
  &L(\hat{y}, y) = -\log \left|y/2 - 1/2 + \hat{y}\right|, \{-1,+1\}
